97
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:26,083
- So what were you
and Kaori talking about?

98
00:05:26,166 --> 00:05:27,625
KOUSEI: Huh? Oh.

99
00:05:27,708 --> 00:05:29,583
[chuckles]
