- Why would you even think that?

106
00:05:44,333 --> 00:05:47,041
There are tons
of good things about you.

107
00:05:47,125 --> 00:05:48,500
Ask anyone.

108
00:05:48,583 --> 00:05:49,750
Like the way you...

109
00:05:49,833 --> 00:05:52,083
uh...

110
00:05:52,166 --> 00:05:53,166
- Ah!
- [gasps]

111
00:05:53,250 --> 00:05:55,125
- [laughs]

112
00:05:55,208 --> 00:05:57,791
Would you look at that, Kousei!

113
00:05:57,875 --> 00:05:59,458
