117
00:06:13,208 --> 00:06:15,583
- Incoming!
- [screams]

118
00:06:15,666 --> 00:06:18,833
- Dude, tell me you saw
that goal I just made!

119
00:06:18,916 --> 00:06:20,291
- Are you trying to kill me?

120
00:06:20,375 --> 00:06:21,833
- [grunts]
- [camera whirs]

121
00:06:21,916 --> 00:06:22,958
- Huh?

122
00:06:23,041 --> 00:06:23,791
- I'm texting it to Kaori.

123
00:06:23,875 --> 00:06:25,000
- What?

124
00:06:25,083 --> 00:06:27,500
- You wanna go see her tomorrow?

125
00:06:27,583 --> 00:06:30,375
