letting her out.

126
00:06:30,458 --> 00:06:32,166
Yeah, we can bring her a gift.

127
00:06:33,666 --> 00:06:35,958
-<i> Of course he has her number.</i>

128
00:06:36,041 --> 00:06:38,458
- I bet she'll dig that.
Don't you think?

129
00:06:40,416 --> 00:06:41,916
- I'm gonna pass,

130
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,666
but you should
totally still do it.

131
00:06:46,875 --> 00:06:49,166
I'd feel out of place.

132
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,875
