the competition for her.

133
00:06:52,958 --> 00:06:55,208
Remember?

134
00:06:56,458 --> 00:06:57,708
I failed her.

135
00:06:57,791 --> 00:07:01,916
- Dude, you're the one
she turned to, you know?

136
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:04,875
