139
00:07:15,583 --> 00:07:17,375
What else could it be?

140
00:07:17,458 --> 00:07:18,833
- Yeah, I know.

141
00:07:18,916 --> 00:07:20,125
But look on the bright side.

142
00:07:20,208 --> 00:07:23,583
Attention from a pretty girl
is good, no matter what's up.

143
00:07:26,416 --> 00:07:28,625
