don't skip out 'cause of me.

144
00:07:28,708 --> 00:07:30,375
Let's go together.

145
00:07:30,458 --> 00:07:32,541
Maybe we see more sponge bath.

146
00:07:32,625 --> 00:07:33,583
COACH: Hustle, Watari!

147
00:07:33,666 --> 00:07:34,833
You're the captain, remember?!

148
00:07:34,916 --> 00:07:36,333
- Yeah, Coach!

149
00:07:36,416 --> 00:07:38,333
Stick around,
and watch me knock 'em dead.

150
00:07:38,416 --> 00:07:40,000
- Look who's feeling cocky.

151
00:07:40,083 --> 00:07:41,791
- You know it, man.

152
00:07:41,875 --> 00:07:43,666
Gotta end my middle school
career on a high note.

153
00:07:45,583 --> 00:07:46,833
Truth of it is,

154
00:07:46,916 --> 00:07:48,833
watching the two of you
play with such spirit

155
00:07:48,916 --> 00:07:50,708
kind of got me
all fired up myself.

156
00:07:53,375 --> 00:07:55,166
That moment was awesome.

157
00:07:55,250 --> 00:07:57,125
I don't think
I could ever forget it.

158
00:08:01,833 --> 00:08:04,250
<i>Don't think</i>
<i>I could ever forget it.</i>

159
00:08:05,833 --> 00:08:08,500
<i>- Do you think</i>
<i>you can just forget it?</i>

160
00:08:14,958 --> 00:08:17,083
[rain pattering]

161
00:08:23,166 --> 00:08:25,250
<i>The piano</i>
<i>is just one part of you,</i>

162
00:08:25,333 --> 00:08:28,541
<i>but in that moment, I knew...</i>

163
00:08:29,958 --> 00:08:32,333
<i>it was your entire universe.</i>

164
00:08:32,416 --> 00:08:33,916
[running footsteps splashing]

165
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,125
<i>You're trying to rip it away</i>
<i>and leave it behind.</i>

166
00:08:36,208 --> 00:08:38,750
<i>I see you tear at it,</i>

167
00:08:38,833 --> 00:08:43,000
<i>and the pain, it's more</i>
<i>than you can hope to bear.</i>

168
00:08:44,458 --> 00:08:46,041
<i>It eats at you.</i>

169
00:08:46,125 --> 00:08:49,125
<i>You hide it,</i>
<i>but your face is an open book.</i>

170
00:08:54,208 --> 00:08:56,750
<i>You think you can forget?</i>

171
00:08:56,833 --> 00:08:58,416
[audience cheering]

172
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:01,125
<i>No way. Not a chance.</i>

173
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:03,875
<i>'Cause that moment,</i>

174
00:09:03,958 --> 00:09:06,000
<i>that's what you and I</i>
<i>are living for.</i>

175
00:09:07,208 --> 00:09:08,291
[audience cheering]

176
00:09:08,375 --> 00:09:11,958
<i>- You kids are unbelievable!</i>

177
00:09:12,041 --> 00:09:12,583
<i>- That was awesome!</i>

178
00:09:12,666 --> 00:09:15,000
<i>- Encore! Encore!</i>

179
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:23,750
KAORI:<i> You and I,</i>
<i>we have music in our bones.</i>

180
00:09:28,041 --> 00:09:29,458
- [yelps]

181
00:09:29,541 --> 00:09:30,958
- [chuckles] Oh, easy does it.

182
00:09:31,041 --> 00:09:33,458
[chuckles]

183
00:09:35,875 --> 00:09:39,916
- Well, we're not winning
any points on technique today.

184
00:09:41,208 --> 00:09:43,666
Even so, in some tiny way,

185
00:09:43,750 --> 00:09:47,416
these people aren't ever
going to forget about us.

186
00:09:51,666 --> 00:09:52,666
I'll never forget about us.

187
00:10:01,416 --> 00:10:03,000
No matter what happens.

188
00:10:03,083 --> 00:10:03,666
[cheering continues]

189
00:10:08,333 --> 00:10:09,625
Thank you.

190
00:10:10,541 --> 00:10:11,500
You gave me this.

191
00:10:11,583 --> 00:10:14,833
You came out here
and played with me

192
00:10:14,916 --> 00:10:16,583
when every instinct
told you not to.

193
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:26,083
Oh, Kousei, thank you so much.

194
00:10:36,791 --> 00:10:37,833
KOUSEI:<i> She's a force of nature.</i>

195
00:10:40,416 --> 00:10:42,500
<i>She stares right through me.</i>

196
00:10:43,791 --> 00:10:46,000
<i>And whether I like it or not,</i>

197
00:10:46,083 --> 00:10:49,000
<i>she trusts that I'm</i>
<i>right behind her.</i>

198
00:10:50,208 --> 00:10:53,000
-<i> Believe in me.</i>

199
00:10:55,750 --> 00:11:00,666
<i>- The one who needed</i>
<i>believing in was me.</i>

200
00:11:02,375 --> 00:11:03,666
<i>Thank you.</i>

201
00:11:04,166 --> 00:11:06,333
<i>Thank you.</i>

202
00:11:08,458 --> 00:11:10,541
[thump]

203
00:11:16,250 --> 00:11:19,083
[rain pattering]

204
00:11:21,833 --> 00:11:23,666
- I see.

205
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:26,708
I guess I passed out again.

206
00:11:28,708 --> 00:11:29,750
[rain pattering]

207
00:11:31,625 --> 00:11:32,625
[student chatter]

208
00:11:32,708 --> 00:11:35,458
[metal bat rings]

