00:11:35,541 --> 00:11:36,666
- Heads up!

210
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:37,750
[gasps]

211
00:11:37,833 --> 00:11:38,750
- Safe!

212
00:11:38,833 --> 00:11:39,875
- [moaning]

213
00:11:42,916 --> 00:11:45,416
- Come on, Tsubaki!
Get your head in the game!

214
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:48,958
- Yeah, I know!
- Oh, give me a break.

215
00:11:49,041 --> 00:11:50,416
BOY: Here goes!

216
00:11:51,916 --> 00:11:54,833
- Little kids are so gung-ho.
- What you waiting for?

217
00:11:54,916 --> 00:11:57,083
- He's gotta be freezing
his butt off down there.

218
00:11:57,166 --> 00:11:59,041
- You know, it wasn't
so long ago you'd have

219
