00:12:02,333 --> 00:12:03,708
- Just about drowned poor Arima.

222
00:12:03,791 --> 00:12:06,083
WATARI: Kousei!

223
00:12:06,166 --> 00:12:07,416
TSUBAKI: Oh, whatever.

224
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:10,041
He had a great time
once he was in the water.

225
00:12:10,125 --> 00:12:12,750
KASHIWAGI: Wonder if he'd
agree with you.

226
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,291
-<i> Of course he would.</i>

227
00:12:20,375 --> 00:12:22,000
<i>There's no doubt in my mind.</i>

228
00:12:24,041 --> 00:12:26,166
[footsteps shuffling]

229
00:12:28,333 --> 00:12:29,458
KASHIWAGI: Did something
happen with you two?

230
00:12:29,541 --> 00:12:32,083
- [gasps] Did something happen?!

231
