tearing it up out there?

248
00:13:13,958 --> 00:13:16,041
- [laughs] Kicking ass
and taking names.

249
00:13:16,125 --> 00:13:17,333
How 'bout you?

250
00:13:17,416 --> 00:13:19,375
- It's tough being
a first-year again.

251
